---
// What We Do Section - Combined Story
// Start with the right question → Layered methodology diagram → How we do it
---

<section class="what-we-do section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 class="big-bold-text">START WITH THE RIGHT QUESTION.</h2>

    <p class="intro-text">
      We don't just build what you ask for. We discover what your business actually needs. Every product is different. Every business has unique patterns. We don't rush discovery—we do it right.
    </p>

    <!-- Compact Layered Diagram -->
    <div class="methodology-diagram">
      <h3 class="diagram-title">Our Methodology: Product Surface Foundation</h3>
      <p class="diagram-subtitle">Starting from your business foundation, we layer discovery:</p>

      <div class="layers-stack">
        <div class="layer base-layer">
          <span class="layer-label">Product Surface Foundation</span>
        </div>
        <div class="layer">
          <span class="layer-num">01</span>
          <span class="layer-label">Communication</span>
        </div>
        <div class="layer">
          <span class="layer-num">02</span>
          <span class="layer-label">Problem Statement</span>
        </div>
        <div class="layer">
          <span class="layer-num">03</span>
          <span class="layer-label">Goal & Expectation</span>
        </div>
        <div class="layer">
          <span class="layer-num">04</span>
          <span class="layer-label">User Requirement</span>
        </div>
        <div class="layer">
          <span class="layer-num">05</span>
          <span class="layer-label">Workflow</span>
        </div>
        <div class="layer data-layer">
          <span class="layer-num">06</span>
          <span class="layer-label">Data Foundation</span>
          <div class="data-pills">
            <span>Management</span>
            <span>Quality</span>
            <span>Privacy</span>
            <span>Compliance</span>
            <span>Steward</span>
            <span>Governance</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="layer-descriptions">
        <p><strong>Product Surface Foundation:</strong> Your business patterns, user needs, and technical constraints form the base every layer builds upon.</p>
        <p><strong>01 Communication:</strong> Aligning stakeholders on vision and goals</p>
        <p><strong>02 Problem Statement:</strong> Defining what we're really solving</p>
        <p><strong>03 Goal & Expectation:</strong> What success looks like for your business</p>
        <p><strong>04 User Requirement:</strong> What users actually need to succeed</p>
        <p><strong>05 Workflow:</strong> How this will work in practice</p>
        <p><strong>06 Data Foundation:</strong> Comprehensive data governance covering management, quality, privacy, compliance, stewardship, and ongoing monitoring</p>
      </div>

      <p class="methodology-note">
        Each layer builds on validated insights, not assumptions.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Three Steps - After Diagram -->
    <div class="how-we-do-it">
      <h3 class="section-subtitle">How We Do It:</h3>

      <div class="steps">
        <div class="step">
          <span class="step-number">1</span>
          <h4 class="step-title">Foundation Discovery</h4>
          <p class="step-description">
            We dig into your business patterns to refine your problem statement. Together, we define your product's goals and expectations—the foundation everything else is built on.
          </p>
          <p class="step-deliverable">
            <strong>What you get:</strong> Clear problem definition, validated business goals, project expectations documented
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="step">
          <span class="step-number">2</span>
          <h4 class="step-title">Proof of Concept & Research</h4>
          <p class="step-description">
            We plan and conduct research with your real end-users. Through structured interviews and testing, we validate assumptions and uncover requirements you didn't know you had.
          </p>
          <p class="step-deliverable">
            <strong>What you get:</strong> User insights from actual interviews, validated requirements, research documentation
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="step">
          <span class="step-number">3</span>
          <h4 class="step-title">Deliverables</h4>
          <p class="step-description">
            You receive your first prototype sketch and a comprehensive Business Requirements Specification (BRS)—complete with KPIs. This becomes your roadmap for development.
          </p>
          <p class="step-deliverable">
            <strong>What you get:</strong> Initial prototype, firm BRS with documented KPIs, development-ready specifications
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="ai-note">
      <strong>Note on AI:</strong> We use Generative AI to draft documents and prototypes—but never for thinking. Every insight, every decision, every strategy comes from human analysis of your unique business.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .what-we-do {
    background-color: var(--color-primary);
  }

  .what-we-do .big-bold-text {
    color: var(--color-white);
  }

  .intro-text {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-4xl);
    text-align: center;
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
  }

  /* Compact Layered Diagram */
  .methodology-diagram {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: var(--space-4xl) auto;
  }

  .diagram-title {
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-white);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .diagram-subtitle {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3xl);
  }

  .layers-stack {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 4px;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto var(--space-2xl);
  }

  .layer {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    padding: var(--space-sm) var(--space-lg);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    min-height: 48px;
    position: relative;
    transition: all var(--transition-base);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
  }

  .layer::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 6px;
    background: linear-gradient(to bottom,
      transparent 0%,
      var(--color-accent-warm) 40%,
      var(--color-accent-warm) 100%
    );
    border-radius: 0 0 var(--radius-sm) var(--radius-sm);
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  .layer:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .layer:hover::after {
    opacity: 1;
    height: 8px;
  }

  .base-layer {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.18);
    border: 2px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
    padding: var(--space-md) var(--space-xl);
    min-height: 60px;
  }

  .base-layer::after {
    height: 10px;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .base-layer .layer-label {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-white);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .layer-num {
    width: 28px;
    height: 28px;
    background: var(--color-accent-warm);
    color: var(--color-white);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 700;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .layer-label {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-white);
    flex: 1;
  }

  .data-layer {
    min-height: auto;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .data-pills {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: var(--space-xs);
    flex: 1;
  }

  .data-pills span {
    padding: 4px 12px;
    background: transparent;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-accent-cool);
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    color: var(--color-accent-cool);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .layer-descriptions {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: var(--space-3xl) auto var(--space-2xl);
    padding: var(--space-2xl);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  }

  .layer-descriptions p {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .layer-descriptions p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .layer-descriptions strong {
    color: var(--color-white);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .methodology-note {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-accent-cool);
    margin-top: var(--space-2xl);
  }

  /* How We Do It Section */
  .how-we-do-it {
    margin-top: var(--space-4xl);
  }

  .section-subtitle {
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-white);
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-3xl);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .steps {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
    gap: var(--space-3xl);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-4xl);
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .step {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    padding: var(--space-2xl);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    transition: all var(--transition-base);
  }

  .step:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
    border-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.25);
  }

  .step-number {
    width: 40px;
    height: 40px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    background-color: var(--color-accent-warm);
    color: var(--color-white);
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .step-title {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-white);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .step-description {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .step-deliverable {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
    padding: var(--space-md) 0 var(--space-md) var(--space-md);
    background-color: transparent;
    border-radius: 0;
    border-left: 2px solid var(--color-accent-cool);
  }

  .step-deliverable strong {
    color: var(--color-accent-cool);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }

  .ai-note {
    max-width: 700px;
    margin: var(--space-4xl) auto 0;
    padding: var(--space-xl);
    background: rgba(100, 181, 246, 0.1);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    border: 2px solid var(--color-accent-cool);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    color: var(--color-white);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .ai-note strong {
    color: var(--color-accent-cool);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .layer {
      padding: var(--space-sm) var(--space-md);
      min-height: 44px;
    }

    .base-layer {
      padding: var(--space-sm) var(--space-md);
      min-height: 52px;
    }

    .layer-descriptions {
      padding: var(--space-lg);
    }

    .layer-descriptions p {
      font-size: var(--text-sm);
    }

    .steps {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-xl);
    }

    .step {
      padding: var(--space-lg);
    }
  }
</style>
